tourBios.curYrHigh: Finished T33 with two others at the Mainland China Qualifying Tournament to earn conditional-exempt status for the PGA TOUR China Series' season.
tourBios.carHigh:
2014: Made appearances in all 12 PGA TOUR China Series' tournaments, missing the cut in 11 and withdrawing from the Jianye Tianzhu Henan Open. 
2013: Missed the cut at the China Masters and withdrew from the Foshan Open and the GS Caltex Maekyung Open…On the PGA Tour of Australasia, missed the cut. 
2012: Finished T47 at the Nanshan China Masters in mid-October, along with fellow countryman Ouyang Zheng…At the Saint Omer Open, missed the cut after consecutive 82s. 
2011: Despite a 74-72 opening 36 holes, missed the cut at the Volvo China Open. 
2010: Missed the cut at the China Open. 
2009: Missed the cut in the inaugural OneAsia Tour event, the Volvo China Open (18-over).

dyn.dynStats: He ranks T11th in Victory Leaders on the PGA Tour China Series.
